"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"黨鐵 屌你老母 要還嫁！"},{"pid":"199a0eae13d1cc6a1874b0a6f011b4a862c2ea6f","tid":1523303,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b5e636ad6e664cc5be486451e1f81c0ae0e70b","tid":1523303,"uid":274145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"推啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f2f17d01a81e0cf5d08bcd947e2e525394230b26","tid":1523303,"uid":274145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"幫推😭😭"},{"pid":"fe1590f18cbc58bc4e2f08f6e6def89d0b4d87d1","tid":1523303,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"地鐵公司驚條撚 <br />\n次次逃走都沖去搭地鐵<br />\n香港人好似唔識搭巴士咁樣"},{"pid":"3701037422121faf525eb0eb8eeaaf9e6fd50281","tid":1523303,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c48be791fa43ad980464d96d6602ddea44355a","tid":1523303,"uid":25573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"831黑警恐襲，血債血償！！！！"},{"pid":"09705745b06578221fdbd2372a76534e50d7d4a6","tid":1523303,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0